org.batfish.question

Class ReachabilityParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.question.ReachabilityParameters

  • public final class ReachabilityParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    A set of parameters for reachability analysis that uses high-level specifiers. It is a good choice for questions because relatively little work is needed to map user input into it.
